    Multiply Linear Regression

    my_lm.Rd

    Multiply Linear Regression

    Usage

    my_lm(formula, data)

    Arguments

    formula

    11

    data

    1111

    Value

    List containing the following elements

    • beta estimates(coefficients)

    • fitted_values

    • residuals

    • rsquared

    Examples

    data = mtcars
formula = mpg ~ disp + hp
my_lm(formula, data)
